snippet.title: Prince Charles Denies Claims He Speculated On Archie’s Skin Colour
snippet.description:
A spokesperson for Prince Charles is dismissing allegations, made in a passage of the new book ‘Brothers and Wives: Inside the Lives of William, Kate, Harry and Meghan’, claiming he made comments about the complexion of the Duke and Duchess of Sussex’s son Archie before he was born. ET Canada's Sangita Patel and Morgan Hoffman react.
#PrinceCharles #PrinceHarry #MeghanMarkle
